Custom routes.

USAGE:
  scw vpc route <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  create         Create a Route
  delete         Delete a Route
  enable-routing Enable routing on a VPC
  get            Get a Route
  list           Return routes with associated next hop data
  update         Update Route

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for route
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw vpc route [command] --help" for more information about a command.
